#

Zesty Ginger Cookies

$8.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 24

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Tags:

dessertbakingcookie

Description

A delightful blend of ginger and spice, these cookies are both comforting and invigorating.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • ground ginger: 1 tablespoon
  • ground cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • baking soda: 2 teaspoons
  • unsalted butter: 3/4 cup
  • brown sugar: 1 cup
  • molasses: 1/4 cup
  • large egg: 1
  • granulated sugar: 1/4 cup
